Yes — here are the two _meta.yml files.

templates/partials/060-language-keyboard/_meta.yml

title: Language and keyboard
order: 60
required: true
selection: one
default: us_english
description: Sets the operating system language and keyboard layout used during and after installation.
applies_to:
  os:
    - rhel7
    - rhel8
    - rhel9
    - rhel10
  profiles:
    - minimal
    - small_disk
    - developer_workstation
options:
  - id: us_english
    file: us-english.ks.j2
    title: US English
    description: Uses US English as the system language and a standard US keyboard layout.
    recommended: true
    risk: low
    warning: ""
notes: >
  Most AeroLIT environments should use this default unless a site specifically
